003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高黎瓦:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e   我操你妈，老子18岁证明出来的东西你们花了60年才看懂？？？？？研究这个鬼东西害的老子他妈的高考都没考上！！！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e蓝翔技师学院:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e    恭喜校友证明那个哥什么赫猜想！校友牛逼！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e新闻记者:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e     震惊！蓝翔技师学院破格入选双一流！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560262500,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fbadc7812cee84d5ff986df348580b32","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560262500","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545823936,"updated_time":1545823936,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":119,"content":"\u003cp\u003e都能证明哥德巴赫猜想了，还会在提这种无聊的问题的时候，把清华的数学系放在北大之前么？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559475690,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"811cadcc15788e585c24e249e711ead3","url_token":"dong-ri-zhi-yang-48","name":"冬日之阳","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/eff23fdf6dc55dff4ab59692af6bed47_is.jpg","avatar_url_